d","count":1},{"word":"matter","count":1},{"word":"hard","count":1},{"word":"tried","count":1},{"word":"regarded","count":1},{"word":"someone","count":1},{"word":"standing","count":1},{"word":"shadow","count":1},{"word":"supposed","count":1},{"word":"rival","count":1},{"word":"eventually","count":1},{"word":"surpass","count":1},{"word":"spent","count":1},{"word":"days","count":1},{"word":"studying","count":1},{"word":"pushing","count":1},{"word":"exams","count":1},{"word":"prove","count":1},{"word":"outstanding","count":1},{"word":"verge","count":1},{"word":"surpassing","count":1},{"word":"said","count":1},{"word":"pursue","count":1},{"word":"real","count":1},{"word":"passion","count":1},{"word":"bastard","count":1},{"word":"remain","count":1},{"word":"undefeated","count":1},{"word":"forever","count":1},{"word":"waited","count":1},{"word":"month","count":1},{"word":"week","count":1},{"word":"could've","count":1},{"word":"shown","count":1},{"word":"looked","count":1},{"word":"must","count":1},{"word":"joking","count":1},{"word":"create","count":1},{"word":"accept","count":1},{"word":"betrayal","count":1},{"word":"academic","count":1},{"word":"potential","count":1},{"word":"silly","count":1},{"word":"managed","count":1},{"word":"become","count":1},{"word":"success","count":1},{"word":"guy","count":1},{"word":"thought","count":1},{"word":"becoming","count":1},{"word":"professor","count":1},{"word":"equal","count":1},{"word":"took","count":1},{"word":"seriously","count":1},{"word":"wait","count":1},{"word":"really","count":1},{"word":"grin","count":1},{"word":"definitely","count":1},{"word":"tsk","count":1},{"word":"knew","count":1},{"word":"slacker","count":1},{"word":"grinding","count":1},{"word":"behind","count":1},{"word":"along","count":1},{"word":"natural","count":1},{"word":"talent","count":1},{"word":"try","count":1},{"word":"fine","count":1},{"word":"chance","count":1},{"word":"straight","count":1},{"word":"i'll","count":1},{"word":"use","count":1},{"word":"face","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"...Well done, {PlayerName}. I admit defeat.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"As agreed, I will withdraw the application to disband the fan club. But for your own good, and for the Academy's... I urge you to stop playing that cursed game.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"...Yes. The man who threw away his future, betrayed his studies, and neglected his responsibilities, all to indulge in pleasure...","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Is none other than the man calling himself the founder of Peaks of Prestige, Furius!","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"It's the truth. We went to school together... long before I ever came to this Academy.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Don't let his carefree act fool you. He was once a brilliant student. He was the one who should've ended up at the Academy, not me.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Though I hate to admit it, before he threw it all away, he was considered a genius by many...","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Top marks without even trying. The teachers always praised him for it.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"As for me... No matter how hard I tried, I was always regarded as someone standing in his shadow.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"But it wasn't supposed to be like that! He was meant to be my rival! The one I would eventually surpass and defeat!","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"I spent all my days studying, pushing myself to beat him in exams and prove to everyone that I was the most outstanding student!","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"...Just when I was on the verge of finally surpassing him, he just... dropped out of school!","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"He said he was going back to Septimont to \"pursue his real passion.\" That bastard... it meant he'd remain undefeated forever!","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"If only he'd waited another month... No, another week! I could've shown everyone what defeat looked like on him!","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"You must be joking... Furius dropped out to create that Peaks of Prestige, did he not?!","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"I will never accept that! It's a betrayal of his academic potential... How infuriating that his silly game managed to become a success, too!","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"That guy... I thought becoming a professor here would finally make him see me as an equal, but he never took me seriously. Not once...","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"...What?","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Wait... Was that really Furius? No, that infuriating grin... that was definitely him.","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Tsk, I knew it... He may look like a slacker, but he was grinding behind my back all along. So he wasn't just some natural talent who didn't need to try...","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019},{"text":"Fine! Once I get the chance, I'm going straight to Septimont. I'll use his own Peaks of Prestige to beat him at his own game, and make him admit defeat to my face!","quest_name":"Peaks of Prestige: Rekindled Duel","quest_id":192700019}]}